# Risk
### v0.2

This data standard represents how risks are recorded with MHCLG. This aligns to the MHCLG’s [Risk Management Framework](https://mhclg.sharepoint.com/sites/RiskKnowledgeCentre/SitePages/Risk-Management-Framework.aspx) which sets out the Departments approach to managing risk in order to:

- protect our people
- protect our reputation
- protect against financial loss
- minimise disruption to the programmes which achieve our objectives

